jobs.title: FrontEndDeveloper
jobs.description: We are looking for a skilled Front-End Developer to join our dynamic team. You will be responsible for implementing visual elements that users see and interact with in a web application. You should have a strong understanding of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, as well as experience with popular frameworks like React or Angular.
Requirements: Proven experience as a Front-End Developer or similar role
Strong proficiency in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
Experience with React, Angular, or Vue.js
Familiarity with responsive design and cross-browser compatibility
Good problem-solving skills and attention to detail

jobs.title: BackEndDeveloper
jobs.description: We are seeking a talented Back-End Developer to join our team. You will be responsible for server-side web application logic and integration of the front-end part. A basic understanding of front-end technologies is also required.
Requirements: Proven experience as a Back-End Developer or similar role
Strong proficiency in server-side languages such as Node.js, Python, Ruby, or Java
Experience with database management systems like MySQL, PostgreSQL, or MongoDB
Familiarity with RESTful API design and development
Excellent problem-solving skills and ability to work in a team

jobs.title: FullStackDeveloper
jobs.description: We are looking for a Full-Stack Developer to work on both the front-end and back-end of our web applications. You should be comfortable with multiple programming languages and frameworks, and have a passion for building efficient and scalable web applications.
Requirements: Proven experience as a Full-Stack Developer or similar role
Proficiency in front-end technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and frameworks like React or Angular
Strong knowledge of back-end technologies such as Node.js, Python, Ruby, or Java
Experience with database management systems like MySQL, PostgreSQL, or MongoDB
Ability to work independently and in a team environment
